item.title: nanogallery updated to version 5.0.3
item.description:
Image gallery simplified. nanoGALLERY is an easy to implement image gallery plugin for jQuery. It is touch enabled, responsive, fast and it supports cloud storage. Featuring multi-level navigation in albums, lightbox, combinable hover effects on thumbnails, slideshow, fullscreen, pagination, image lazy load, themes, deep linking, browser back/forward navigation, i18n, and pulling in Flickr, Picasa, Google+ and SmugMug photo albums among others.

//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/nanogallery/5.0.3/jquery.nanogallery.min.js
item.dc:creator: cdnjs team

item.title: gsap updated to version 1.13.2
item.description:
GreenSock Animation Platform (GSAP) is a suite of tools for scripted animation, including TweenLite, TweenMax, TimelineLite, TimelineMax, various easing equations (EasePack), plugins for things like animating along Bezier paths, tweening RaphaelJS objects, etc. and it also includes a jQuery plugin that hijacks the native jQuery.animate() method so that animations perform much better and additional properties can be tweened, like colors, transforms (2D and 3D), boxShadow, borderRadius, clip, and lots more. GSAP has no dependencies on jQuery and it can animate ANY numeric property of ANY object.

//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/1.13.2/TweenMax.min.js
item.dc:creator: cdnjs team
